title: Password Reset Link Not Working
description: User has attempted to use the password reset feature multiple times, but the link sent to their email is consistently expired or invalid.

title: Issue with API Authentication
description: A developer reports that their API key is not authenticating correctly, receiving a 401 Unauthorized error despite the key being correct.

title: Incorrect Product Description on Website
description: Customer noticed that the product description for 'Product X' lists the wrong specifications and features.

title: Slow Page Load Times
description: Multiple users have reported that the dashboard page is taking an unusually long time to load, often timing out on slower connections.

title: Missing Order in History
description: Customer confirms a successful payment but their order is not appearing in their purchase history on their account.

title: Billing Dispute - Double Charge
description: Customer's credit card was charged twice for the same monthly subscription renewal. They need a refund for the extra charge.

title: Unable to Upload Profile Picture
description: User reports that uploading a new profile picture results in an error message saying 'File type not supported'.

title: Mobile App Crashes on Login
description: Several users have reported that the iOS mobile app crashes immediately after entering login credentials.

title: Report Export Generates Empty File
description: Customer trying to export a sales report receives an empty CSV file with no data inside.

title: Notifications Not Sent
description: System notifications are not being delivered to users for order confirmations and account updates.

title: Search Function Not Returning Results
description: Search bar returns no results even when searching for existing products and customers.

title: Account Locked After Failed Attempts
description: Customer got locked out of their account after three failed login attempts and is unable to unlock it.
